 Prompt 5 – Personalised Reply

## Version 1 (v5.1)

### Prompt
“Reply to this message [Client Message]”

### Change Made
Initial version

### Observed Effect
Generic instruction with no context and basic reply with no personalisation
Low engagement and not aligned with B2B sales approach

### Lesson Learned
Personalisation is critical in B2B communication


## Version 2 (v5.2)

### Prompt
Think of yourself a B2B sales consultant. Reply to this inquiry: [CLIENT_MESSAGE]. Tailor the response to needs, business stage, and urgency. Also include relevant solution and clear next step. Keep consultative and concise.  

### Change Made
Added role the B2B consultant
needs, stage, urgency were inclded 
Required a solution and next a step
Added tone constrainte

### Observed Effect
More human-like responses and improved engagement potential

### Lesson Learned
More Context and structure gives high-quality personalised output
